comments: During the pick, Hield (SAC) and Theis (BOS) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Theis (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Fox (SAC).
Williams (BOS) dislodges Barnes (SAC) from his legally obtained position.
Holmes (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Theis (BOS) and makes clean ball contact on his dislodge attempt.
Holmes (SAC) makes contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) collapses his arm against Green's (BOS) body and keeps the other arm vertical as he cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Marginal contact occurs as Tatum (BOS) defends Barnes (SAC) off ball.
Teague (BOS) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
During the rebound, Holmes (SAC) and Theis (BOS) engage and disengage prior to Holmes cleanly tapping the ball back to his team.
Green (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position on Hield (SAC) off ball. Hield loses his balance on his own and not as a result of any contact with Green.
The 24 second shot clock expires prior to the ball going out of bounds.
During the inbound, Williams (BOS) and Haliburton (SAC) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Haliburton (SAC) makes contact to Williams' (BOS) arm prior to his pass.
Williams (BOS) steps over the plane of the free throw line before his free throw attempt makes contact with the rim or backboard.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
